org.batfish.storage

Interface StorageProvider

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FileBasedStorage

    @ParametersAreNonnullByDefault
public interface StorageProvider
    Storage backend for loading and storing persistent data used by Batfish

      • loadMajorIssueConfigs

        @Nonnull
Map<String,MajorIssueConfig> loadMajorIssueConfigs(String network,
                                                            Set<String> majorIssueTypes)
        Returns the MajorIssueConfigs for the given network and majorIssueTypes, keyed by major issue type. If no config exists for a given major issue type, will return a mapping whose value is a MajorIssueConfig with an empty list of MinorIssueConfigs

        network - The name of the network
        majorIssueTypes - The types of the major issues whose configurations are to be loaded
